OL,3,CBBC reportedly calls in police to
OL,4,Cinvestigate fresh Strictly allegations
OL,6,FThe BBC has asked the police to
OL,7,Finvestigate fresh allegations
OL,8,Finvolving hit show Strictly Come
OL,9,FDancing, after claims two of its stars
OL,10,Fused cocaine, reports have said.
OL,12,FAccording to the Sun On Sunday, the
OL,13,FBBC has alerted the Metropolitan
OL,14,FPolice to new allegations about the
OL,15,Fshow - but the details have not been
OL,16,Fspecified.
OL,18,FA BBC spokesperson said on Saturday
OL,19,Fthe corporation does not comment on
OL,20,Fpolice investigations.
