OL,3,CBBC reportedly calls in police to
OL,4,Cinvestigate fresh Strictly allegations
OL,6,FEarlier this month, reports in The Sun
OL,7,Falleged two Strictly cast members'
OL,8,Fdrug use was discussed on the BBC
OL,9,Fdancing show, and said that the
OL,10,Fcorporation had appointed law firm
OL,11,FPinsent Masons to lead the
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,FThe scandal-hit show was also the
OL,15,Fsubject of a review in 2024, when the
OL,16,FBBC looked into allegations of
OL,17,Fbullying and harassment against former
OL,18,Fprofessional dancer Giovanni Pernice,
OL,19,Fmade by his former dance partner
OL,20,FAmanda Abbington.
