OL,3,CBBC reportedly calls in police to
OL,4,Cinvestigate fresh Strictly allegations
OL,6,FThe corporation upheld some, but not
OL,7,Fall, of the complaints made ` and
OL,8,Fintroduced a series of new measures
OL,9,Faimed at improving welfare.
OL,11,FThis included the introduction of a
OL,12,Fchaperone who is present "at all
OL,13,Ftimes" during training room rehearsals.
OL,15,FEastEnders star James Borthwick was
OL,16,Falso suspended from the BBC after a
OL,17,Fvideo emerged of the actor using a
OL,18,Fdisabled slur on the set of the dance
OL,19,Fprogramme.
