OL,3,CBBC reportedly calls in police to
OL,4,Cinvestigate fresh Strictly allegations
OL,6,FIt is understood that the BBC often
OL,7,Fappoints external law firms to help it
OL,8,Flead investigations.
OL,10,FThe BBC spokesperson previously said:
OL,11,F"We have clear protocols and policies
OL,12,Fin place for dealing with any serious
OL,13,Fcomplaint raised with us.
OL,15,F"We would always encourage people to
OL,16,Fspeak to us if they have concerns. It
OL,17,Fwould not be appropriate for us to
OL,18,Fcomment further."
OL,20,FThe Metropolitan Police has been
OL,21,Fcontacted for comment.
